<p>They recently moved into their new$13M  family home in Encino in the San Fernando Valley of Los Angeles.</p>

<p>Purchasing the spectacular property back in 2019 and they are now finally moving in, after spending recent months in Oklahoma amid the coronavirus pandemic.</p>

